{"tid":2410161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★當局指有網站偽冒「安心出行」app","createTime":"2021-02-16T11:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T12:54:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d61f86a4c805a17cb28f9849855fb63c05127d6","tid":2410161,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"政府資訊科技總監辦公室提醒市民，近日有網站偽冒「安心出行」流動應用程式，並聲稱已將程式改寫供市民下載，資科辦呼籲公眾提高警覺，切勿信以為真。<br />\n<br />\n資科辦發言人表示，不知名的網站或流動應用程式可能帶有電腦病毒或為木馬軟件，構成網絡安全風險，市民切勿登入或下載。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申「安心出行」流動應用程式無須用戶登記，「無大台」，即出行紀錄只存放用戶手機，出行紀錄的比對和提示功能只會在手機程式內進行，個人行蹤不會外洩，絕不構成私隱風險，市民可安心使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575908-20210216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575908-20210216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=01105b4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575908-20210216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=25d3f2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575908-20210216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c90bb889281317f9277bc4de98f8dfb5a1028106","tid":2410161,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c56536fe433a98f68a6365916cf207f6d5979bf","tid":2410161,"uid":324629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid